high_descs: Turn around and walk across the room to face the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the knife on the back of the counter.
Turn around and walk across the room, then turn left and walk forward to face the white table.
Cut the tomato on the table into slices.
Turn left and walk across the room to face the microwave.
Place the knife in the microwave.
Turn right and walk forward to face the tomato at the end of the white table.
Pick up a potato slice on the white table.
Turn left and walk forward to face the fridge on the right.
Cool the tomato slice in the fridge and then remove it
Take a step to the left and face the microwave on the counter.
Place the tomato slice in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: To cool a slice of tomato and place it in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the stove.
Pick up the butterknife on the counter to the left of the stove.
Turn around and head to the white table near the door.
Slice the tomato on the table.
Turn left and move to the microwave to the left of the refrigerator.
Place the butterknife in the microwave.
Turn right and go back to the white table.
Pick up a tomato slice on the white table.
Turn left and go to the refrigerator and face it.
Chill the tomato slice in the refrigerator for a moment and take it back out.
Move to your left to face the microwave again.
Place the chilled tomato slice in to the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled tomato slice into the microwave.

high_descs: Go to the stove
Pick up the butterknife next to the stove
Go to the white table
Cut the tomato on the table
Go to the microwave
Put the butterknife in the microwave
Go to the white table
Pick up a tomato slice
Go to the fridge
Chill the tomato slice
Go to the microwave
Put the tomato slice in the microwave
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled tomato slice and a butterknife in the microwave
